{"tid":1956772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不忿女友人遭調戲 酒吧7男互打3人傷","createTime":"2020-04-03T11:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T12:40:13.000Z","uid":29627,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"63091d3722c9e8dc592c034497751487c018da8d","tid":1956772,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"不忿女友人遭調戲 酒吧7男互打3人傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200403/large/1585876212_387a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200403%2Flarge%2F1585876212_387a.jpg&h=c0a7f61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨3時許，一名33歲姓戴男子，與23歲姓林女友人及兩名男友人，在土瓜灣譚公道一間酒吧喝酒聊天。其間女友人疑被另一枱男酒客調戲，戴男與兩名男友人不忿，雙方發生爭執，男酒客寡不敵眾逃去。<br />\n<br />\n稍後男酒客帶同另外3名同黨回酒吧尋仇，出手打傷戴男等人後逃去，離開前更以現金支付酒錢。戴男與兩名男友人眼鼻受傷，其中一人拒絕送院。警員調查後，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由九龍城刑事調查隊第一隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n政府宣佈酒吧今日下午6時起關閉14日，酒吧女職員表示，想不到停業前會「搞成咁」，指是年輕人鬥氣，又指即將停業會休息兩星期，對沒有收入深感無奈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200403/large/1585876788_c486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200403%2Flarge%2F1585876788_c486.jpg&h=85f1d955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200403/60789943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200403%2F60789943&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=7b31d66e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200403%2F60789943&h=be557ab5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200403/60789943</a>"},{"pid":"cc2df1c361dec5870b12e31837e8e00adb2d6589","tid":1956772,"uid":21141,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"戴男心諗：我都未屌條女就想搶我頭啖湯？"},{"pid":"4982